1
00:00:00,410 --> 00:00:02,140
(All characters, locations,
organizations, and incidents...)

2
00:00:02,140 --> 00:00:03,540
(in this drama are fictional.)

3
00:00:03,540 --> 00:00:05,210
(This production followed
all guidelines for young actors.)

4
00:00:09,580 --> 00:00:10,750
Jung Won will do well, won't she?

5
00:00:13,050 --> 00:00:14,150
She's my daughter.

6
00:00:15,950 --> 00:00:16,960
And...

7
00:00:17,920 --> 00:00:19,660
she's also Jin Tae Seok's daughter.

8
00:00:20,020 --> 00:00:22,030
But this is Jin Tae Seok
we're talking about.

9
00:00:22,760 --> 00:00:26,770
She's tough now, but I'm worried
she can't handle a monster like him.

10
00:00:31,940 --> 00:00:34,240
I've been waiting for someone
of my own flesh and blood like you.

11
00:00:34,870 --> 00:00:36,140
I just have one question.

12
00:00:36,980 --> 00:00:39,280
They say even animals
treasure their young,

13
00:00:40,410 --> 00:00:41,750
so how could you do
what you did to me?

14
00:00:41,750 --> 00:00:44,420
Don't tell me you're really hurt.

15
00:00:45,850 --> 00:00:48,150
If I could drain every last drop
of your blood from my veins,

16
00:00:48,990 --> 00:00:50,260
I would.

17
00:00:51,660 --> 00:00:54,160
I can't stand just knowing...

18
00:00:55,230 --> 00:00:58,060
your blood runs through my veins,
Jin Tae Seok.

19
00:01:02,000 --> 00:01:03,300
Oh, dear...

20
00:01:03,640 --> 00:01:05,140
You really are hurt.

21
00:01:07,640 --> 00:01:11,410
They say a lion will push
its own cubs off a cliff.

22
00:01:11,610 --> 00:01:15,880
Right. They only raise the cubs
that survive to become jungle kings.

23
00:01:16,310 --> 00:01:18,020
Consider it part of the process.

24
00:01:18,020 --> 00:01:19,720
And what if I had died?

25
00:01:21,250 --> 00:01:24,260
I wanted you dead, so I would have
considered it the natural outcome.

26
00:01:27,360 --> 00:01:28,530
But I'm human, too.

27
00:01:29,130 --> 00:01:31,200
I took in Se Hoon,
and he's not even my own son.

28
00:01:31,630 --> 00:01:35,700
How could I be so heartless to you,
my own flesh and blood?

29
00:01:36,200 --> 00:01:38,440
I wanted you to survive
by any means necessary.

30
00:01:38,940 --> 00:01:40,240
And if you were anything like me,

31
00:01:41,470 --> 00:01:43,140
I figured you'd be invincible.

32
00:01:43,940 --> 00:01:47,180
You're worse than an animal,
Jin Tae Seok.

33
00:01:48,280 --> 00:01:50,080
You'd toss aside your own kid
in an instant...

34
00:01:50,420 --> 00:01:52,520
if they had no use
and if they got in your way.

35
00:01:54,220 --> 00:01:55,350
I'm thinking...

36
00:01:58,920 --> 00:02:01,130
of grooming you to be my successor.

37
00:02:01,660 --> 00:02:02,660
You trust me?

38
00:02:03,260 --> 00:02:05,730
I don't trust anyone.
Not even myself.

39
00:02:06,260 --> 00:02:09,070
Then why did you use me
to go after my mother?

40
00:02:09,300 --> 00:02:11,040
I wanted to see...

41
00:02:11,300 --> 00:02:13,440
whether you were more my daughter
than Hye Ra's.

42
00:02:14,410 --> 00:02:16,880
Only Se Mi feels
like a daughter to me.

43
00:02:17,580 --> 00:02:20,510
Accepting you as my daughter...

44
00:02:21,210 --> 00:02:22,210
is still difficult for me.

45
00:02:23,850 --> 00:02:26,820
That, at least, doesn't sound
like a lie.

46
00:02:38,660 --> 00:02:40,200
(Episode 93)

47
00:02:41,470 --> 00:02:43,740
What is it? Did something happen?

48
00:02:46,870 --> 00:02:48,110
It's about Chairman Joo Ha Neul.

49
00:02:49,540 --> 00:02:52,240
I might be put in a position
where I must take him down myself.

50
00:02:53,110 --> 00:02:54,780
Is that what Jin Tae Seok wants?

51
00:02:56,410 --> 00:02:58,420
He said he would back me
as his successor.

52
00:02:59,180 --> 00:03:00,890
He asked if I'd be willing
to take down Joo Ha Neul.

53
00:03:03,020 --> 00:03:04,720
He's just trying to use me
as his hired gun.

54
00:03:06,120 --> 00:03:07,490
He wants to bring down Ha Neul...

55
00:03:08,060 --> 00:03:10,530
so he can become the chairman again.

56
00:03:13,000 --> 00:03:14,800
He's tempting me
with the succession,

57
00:03:15,570 --> 00:03:17,470
dangling it just out of reach.

58
00:03:18,300 --> 00:03:20,200
And he'll sharpen me
into a better weapon for him.

59
00:03:20,910 --> 00:03:22,310
Just like he did to Se Hoon.

60
00:03:24,840 --> 00:03:26,110
That's a tough choice.

61
00:03:26,740 --> 00:03:29,750
It was hard enough being used
as a weapon against you.

62
00:03:30,820 --> 00:03:32,080
And now he wants me to go
after Joo Ha Neul...

63
00:03:33,650 --> 00:03:35,720
Don't you think
you should be honest with him?

64
00:03:39,190 --> 00:03:42,060
(Joo Ha Neul)

65
00:04:12,890 --> 00:04:14,990
He doesn't see me as his daughter.

66
00:04:14,990 --> 00:04:16,290
Not like he does with Se Mi.

67
00:04:18,130 --> 00:04:20,930
That explains how he could do
something so awful.

68
00:04:21,200 --> 00:04:23,030
People say,
"Blood is thicker than water."

69
00:04:23,530 --> 00:04:25,070
I guess it means nothing
to Jin Tae Seok.

70
00:04:25,070 --> 00:04:26,140
It might be because...

71
00:04:26,140 --> 00:04:27,770
you didn’t live with him
when you were a child.

72
00:04:31,480 --> 00:04:33,080
When I was around four, I think?

73
00:04:33,650 --> 00:04:35,350
I thought Madam Gong
was my birth mother.

74
00:04:37,450 --> 00:04:40,750
She left me home alone,
saying she had to meet someone...

75
00:04:41,220 --> 00:04:42,490
at a nearby cafe.

76
00:04:44,220 --> 00:04:47,730
Looking back now, she probably went
to collect on a debt.

77
00:04:48,790 --> 00:04:51,300
She said she'd be back in an hour,

78
00:04:52,400 --> 00:04:54,600
but I must have misheard it
as ten minutes.

79
00:04:57,200 --> 00:04:59,800
And those ten minutes
felt like an eternity.

80
00:05:00,970 --> 00:05:03,940
Mommy!

81
00:05:04,380 --> 00:05:07,880
What is it? What's wrong?
Ha Neul! Why are you crying?

82
00:05:07,880 --> 00:05:09,050
Where is Auntie?

83
00:05:09,050 --> 00:05:11,150
I told you I'd be right back.

84
00:05:11,220 --> 00:05:14,120
But Mommy, you weren't coming...

85
00:05:14,190 --> 00:05:17,190
Oh, sweetheart. Is that right?
I'm so sorry.

86
00:05:17,460 --> 00:05:21,060
Oh, my sweet boy. I'm so, so sorry.

87
00:05:21,130 --> 00:05:22,860
It's okay. There, there. It's okay.

88
00:05:24,130 --> 00:05:28,000
I realized that Madam Gong
wasn't my birth mother...

89
00:05:28,270 --> 00:05:29,930
when I was in the first grade.

90
00:05:33,640 --> 00:05:37,940
I believed
that Madam Gong killed my father...

91
00:05:38,410 --> 00:05:40,010
for 20 long years.

92
00:05:40,680 --> 00:05:41,810
And yet...

93
00:05:44,050 --> 00:05:46,520
some of those memories
still haunt me.

94
00:05:47,590 --> 00:05:50,190
It's not just parents
who have a weak spot for their kids.

95
00:05:51,060 --> 00:05:55,460
Madam Gong isn't your real mom,
but she's that weak spot for you.

96
00:05:56,890 --> 00:05:58,500
As for Jin Tae Seok and me,

97
00:05:58,960 --> 00:06:00,600
we're nothing but a disgrace
to each other.

98
00:06:01,530 --> 00:06:03,270
What does being blood-related
even matter?

99
00:06:04,970 --> 00:06:08,010
He sees himself as pure evil.

100
00:06:08,710 --> 00:06:13,310
He's convinced that evil is power
and that it can never be defeated.

101
00:06:13,910 --> 00:06:16,850
I'm going to start
by shattering that false belief.

102
00:06:34,770 --> 00:06:39,140
Your drawings always have
such depth and intensity.

103
00:06:39,240 --> 00:06:40,640
But there's a softness to them too.

104
00:06:40,810 --> 00:06:44,480
There's nothing like drawing
to clear your head.

105
00:06:45,310 --> 00:06:46,510
Is that supposed to be Jung Won?

106
00:06:48,850 --> 00:06:49,880
It's a self-portrait.

107
00:06:49,880 --> 00:06:51,080
From 25 years ago.

108
00:06:51,350 --> 00:06:53,250
Was that around the time
we got back together?

109
00:06:54,590 --> 00:06:56,020
Do you wish you could go back?

110
00:06:56,990 --> 00:06:58,490
If only I could...

111
00:06:58,490 --> 00:07:01,060
I guess. You were innocent then...

112
00:07:01,830 --> 00:07:04,930
- And shallow.
- and breathtakingly beautiful.

113
00:07:05,630 --> 00:07:07,500
Despicably vile.

114
00:07:07,670 --> 00:07:10,200
Just looking at you
made my heart race.

115
00:07:11,040 --> 00:07:12,700
I mistook a devil like you...

116
00:07:12,770 --> 00:07:16,410
for the man who loved me most
in the world.

117
00:07:16,670 --> 00:07:18,610
What a fool I was.

118
00:07:19,280 --> 00:07:22,210
You’re upset because you were
ousted as chairman, aren’t you?

119
00:07:22,350 --> 00:07:24,280
You left out the "relieved" part.

120
00:07:24,550 --> 00:07:26,050
It's bittersweet.

121
00:07:27,050 --> 00:07:28,320
What are you relieved about?

122
00:07:28,820 --> 00:07:31,060
You know I was never
cut out for business.

123
00:07:31,560 --> 00:07:35,030
I'd rather be painting,
visiting galleries,

124
00:07:35,130 --> 00:07:37,230
and volunteering
with the Kunhyang Association.

125
00:07:37,830 --> 00:07:39,000
That's how I plan to live.

126
00:07:41,670 --> 00:07:43,970
Maybe we could even do
some traveling?

127
00:07:44,900 --> 00:07:46,140
To beautiful places.

128
00:07:47,770 --> 00:07:50,540
With good company, eating good food.

129
00:07:51,010 --> 00:07:53,380
That doesn't sound like
a bad way to live...

130
00:07:53,640 --> 00:07:54,650
for the rest of my life.

131
00:07:55,180 --> 00:07:56,850
And just leave Kunhyang to the kids?

132
00:07:57,720 --> 00:08:01,090
Chairman Joo will do great.
So will Se Hoon.

133
00:08:01,990 --> 00:08:03,090
What about Jung Won?

134
00:08:03,420 --> 00:08:04,420
Jung Won?

135
00:08:05,960 --> 00:08:09,060
She's not quite capable yet,
but she is your blood, after all.

136
00:08:09,560 --> 00:08:12,230
That girl took me down
without a shred of mercy.

137
00:08:13,600 --> 00:08:14,970
She might even become...

138
00:08:15,230 --> 00:08:18,970
your most formidable successor.

139
00:08:20,100 --> 00:08:24,180
As always, you read me like a book.

140
00:08:25,440 --> 00:08:26,510
But, Hye Ra.

141
00:08:29,350 --> 00:08:30,450
I'm still...

142
00:08:30,950 --> 00:08:34,320
too young to be put out to pasture.

143
00:08:35,020 --> 00:08:37,560
I've still got a fire in my belly.

144
00:08:38,560 --> 00:08:39,560
I suppose you are.

145
00:08:40,690 --> 00:08:42,690
You're still going strong.

146
00:08:43,160 --> 00:08:45,000
Kunhyang's chairman is just a title.

147
00:08:45,360 --> 00:08:46,800
The real chairman for life...

148
00:08:47,400 --> 00:08:50,130
is you, Jin Tae Seok.

149
00:08:53,800 --> 00:08:56,240
Now that sounds like my Han Hye Ra.

150
00:08:57,910 --> 00:08:59,080
Jin Tae Seok.

151
00:08:59,740 --> 00:09:01,310
Just you wait.

152
00:09:01,910 --> 00:09:04,780
You'd kill your own flesh and blood
without a second thought,

153
00:09:05,480 --> 00:09:09,120
and as the source of all evil,
you feel no remorse.

154
00:09:09,820 --> 00:09:12,390
I'll be the one to end you
with my own two hands.

155
00:09:13,290 --> 00:09:14,390
In one single blow.

156
00:09:17,830 --> 00:09:19,760
(Kunhyang Group)

157
00:09:20,870 --> 00:09:24,440
Here are the monitoring reports
from each store for the new line.

158
00:09:24,500 --> 00:09:27,040
Design scores,
trend competitiveness,

159
00:09:27,040 --> 00:09:28,640
and the VIP client preview scores...

160
00:09:28,710 --> 00:09:31,440
are all up by over 15 percent
from last season.

161
00:09:32,580 --> 00:09:35,010
Great work, Team Leader Cha.

162
00:09:35,780 --> 00:09:38,880
I spoke with the store managers,
and the response has been amazing.

163
00:09:38,950 --> 00:09:41,490
They're all clamoring
for more inventory.

164
00:09:41,690 --> 00:09:44,160
They say inquiries from customers
are pouring in.

165
00:09:44,160 --> 00:09:45,520
I've got a feeling
this is going to be huge.

166
00:09:45,590 --> 00:09:48,630
Preparing for this season
was a real struggle,

167
00:09:48,730 --> 00:09:51,860
but thanks to you staying strong
and giving it your all,

168
00:09:52,030 --> 00:09:54,100
we managed to overcome the crisis.

169
00:09:54,230 --> 00:09:56,200
You worked hard, too, Director Jin.

170
00:09:56,970 --> 00:09:58,200
Thank you.

171
00:09:58,500 --> 00:10:01,510
So how about a team dinner tonight?

172
00:10:03,670 --> 00:10:05,710
Tonight, it's my treat.

173
00:10:08,610 --> 00:10:10,780
(Damga Charcoal Grill)

174
00:10:17,020 --> 00:10:18,220
Did you already start without me?

175
00:10:19,290 --> 00:10:20,490
I'm a little hurt.

176
00:10:20,990 --> 00:10:22,960
A fired employee has no business
being here.

177
00:10:25,200 --> 00:10:27,870
Come on, we're practically family.

178
00:10:27,870 --> 00:10:29,330
What's the big deal about a meal?

179
00:10:29,330 --> 00:10:30,370
Is it the end of the world?

180
00:10:31,970 --> 00:10:33,270
Just stay for dinner.

181
00:10:34,270 --> 00:10:37,980
It's strange. No matter how much I eat,
I still feel empty.

182
00:10:39,080 --> 00:10:41,880
I can't tell if she's that shameless
or just pretending to be.

183
00:10:42,380 --> 00:10:44,120
How did she know
about the team dinner anyway?

184
00:10:44,520 --> 00:10:46,820
She must have been eavesdropping
somewhere again.

185
00:10:48,120 --> 00:10:49,790
- Looks delicious.
- Oh my!

186
00:10:49,850 --> 00:10:51,360
- Young Chae, your hand!
- Young Chae!

187
00:10:51,360 --> 00:10:52,460
Oh no...

188
00:10:56,560 --> 00:10:59,200
I think I'm going to vomit.
The smell of the meat makes me sick.

189
00:11:04,270 --> 00:11:06,840
When I was pregnant with Se Mi,

190
00:11:07,610 --> 00:11:09,840
I was very sensitive to smells,

191
00:11:10,110 --> 00:11:11,810
but you seem to be fine, Young Chae?

192
00:11:13,110 --> 00:11:15,510
Joo Young Chae, are you okay?

193
00:11:16,350 --> 00:11:18,820
- What?
- Shouldn't you go to the hospital?

194
00:11:19,250 --> 00:11:21,020
It's nothing serious.

195
00:11:22,820 --> 00:11:24,060
You rude brat.

196
00:11:24,460 --> 00:11:26,160
Have you completely lost it?

197
00:11:26,820 --> 00:11:29,190
Was getting fired
that much of a shock?

198
00:11:31,200 --> 00:11:33,330
Something's off with Young Chae.

199
00:11:45,480 --> 00:11:46,840
This can't be happening.

200
00:11:47,610 --> 00:11:48,910
How could this happen?

201
00:11:49,880 --> 00:11:51,320
Why now, of all times?

202
00:11:57,790 --> 00:11:59,690
(Pregnant)

203
00:12:05,500 --> 00:12:07,030
What are you talking about?

204
00:12:07,500 --> 00:12:11,370
You're saying Han Hye Ra
set up this restaurant for me?

205
00:12:11,600 --> 00:12:15,370
It was back when I was still married
to the Kunhyang family.

206
00:12:15,970 --> 00:12:16,970
(Damga Charcoal Grill)

207
00:12:17,110 --> 00:12:18,210
What's this?

208
00:12:19,510 --> 00:12:20,780
It's the contract for a restaurant.

209
00:12:22,210 --> 00:12:25,050
Su A's father won't accept this.
Su A's mother...

210
00:12:27,150 --> 00:12:29,150
I put the lease
in Jo Mi Hyang's name.

211
00:12:29,390 --> 00:12:32,590
She wanted to thank you
for raising me so well.

212
00:12:32,590 --> 00:12:33,960
Goodness.

213
00:12:34,290 --> 00:12:35,830
And I had no idea.

214
00:12:36,130 --> 00:12:40,160
I just thought you did it for me
because you married rich.

215
00:12:40,230 --> 00:12:41,400
But I could do it now.

216
00:12:41,500 --> 00:12:44,440
I've also been gritting my teeth
and saving every cent I make.

217
00:12:44,740 --> 00:12:46,140
I'm going to pay it all back now.

218
00:12:46,500 --> 00:12:48,470
I can't stand being indebted
to Han Hye Ra.

219
00:12:51,110 --> 00:12:52,410
Do you still...

220
00:12:52,910 --> 00:12:55,510
hate former Chairman Han Hye Ra?

221
00:12:55,710 --> 00:12:58,250
What about you?
You don't hate her anymore?

222
00:12:58,850 --> 00:13:01,850
Did all that just go away
because she drank poison for you?

223
00:13:02,150 --> 00:13:03,850
She was honest with me.

224
00:13:04,990 --> 00:13:07,590
It's true she wanted
to abandon me and run.

225
00:13:08,490 --> 00:13:10,730
She also said that she didn't want
to live as a murderer's wife.

226
00:13:12,330 --> 00:13:14,930
She regrets it terribly.

227
00:13:16,100 --> 00:13:17,940
Who lives a life without regrets?

228
00:13:18,540 --> 00:13:20,910
I just feel sorry for your father
who's gone now.

229
00:13:27,580 --> 00:13:28,580
Mom.

230
00:13:30,310 --> 00:13:31,920
My biological father...

231
00:13:35,350 --> 00:13:37,290
is Jin Tae Seok,
the man who killed my dad.

232
00:13:38,760 --> 00:13:39,920
What did you just say?

233
00:13:40,360 --> 00:13:42,130
That's utter nonsense!

234
00:13:42,430 --> 00:13:44,030
I can't believe it either.

235
00:13:45,030 --> 00:13:46,430
But I'm sure.

236
00:13:47,130 --> 00:13:48,630
I even got a DNA test.

237
00:13:51,400 --> 00:13:54,440
Wait. What does that mean?

238
00:13:55,170 --> 00:13:56,170
Then,

239
00:13:56,840 --> 00:13:58,910
before she even met Ki Beom,

240
00:13:59,380 --> 00:14:01,880
was Han Hye Ra already pregnant
with you?

241
00:14:03,450 --> 00:14:04,880
I don't think she knew.

242
00:14:05,750 --> 00:14:07,550
My goodness.

243
00:14:08,090 --> 00:14:10,190
Poor Han Hye Ra. What a life.

244
00:14:10,490 --> 00:14:12,590
I wonder if it's because
I have Jin Tae Seok's blood in me...

245
00:14:13,720 --> 00:14:14,830
that I was so...

246
00:14:15,690 --> 00:14:17,530
desperate to climb so high.

247
00:14:17,830 --> 00:14:20,760
Why must you say
such heartbreaking things?

248
00:14:21,530 --> 00:14:23,700
No one chooses
who their parents are.

249
00:14:24,000 --> 00:14:27,040
The love that raised you matters,
not blood.

250
00:14:29,410 --> 00:14:30,980
No matter what anyone says,

251
00:14:31,610 --> 00:14:33,440
you are my daughter,

252
00:14:33,680 --> 00:14:34,750
as well as the daughter
of the late Ki Beom.

253
00:14:36,980 --> 00:14:41,550
In my entire life, I've never seen
a man as evil as Jin Tae Seok.

254
00:14:42,190 --> 00:14:44,020
To think that monster
is your father.

255
00:14:44,620 --> 00:14:47,260
I just can't accept it.

256
00:14:53,960 --> 00:14:57,330
(Damga Charcoal Grill)

257
00:14:59,900 --> 00:15:02,110
Smells nice.
What did you say this is?

258
00:15:02,110 --> 00:15:03,670
Beef sauvignon?

259
00:15:03,810 --> 00:15:05,410
A French short rib stew, you said?

260
00:15:05,480 --> 00:15:07,410
How much wine...

261
00:15:07,480 --> 00:15:08,780
Is this much okay?

262
00:15:08,850 --> 00:15:11,950
Here. Stir this so it won't burn.

263
00:15:11,950 --> 00:15:13,350
Okay.

264
00:15:20,060 --> 00:15:22,030
This is great. I'm so happy.

265
00:15:23,190 --> 00:15:26,960
Gu Yeong Soo, are you making
the mulled wine or just chugging it?

266
00:15:27,100 --> 00:15:29,830
You're crazy for wine, honestly.

267
00:15:29,900 --> 00:15:31,240
Turn down the heat.

268
00:15:31,570 --> 00:15:33,370
If you boil it too much,
it will taste harsh.

269
00:15:33,700 --> 00:15:38,440
Once it starts steaming,
simmer on low for 20 more minutes.

270
00:15:38,510 --> 00:15:40,110
And then your mulled wine is done.

271
00:15:40,110 --> 00:15:41,880
Are you Grandma now?
Why are you speaking so informally?

272
00:15:42,580 --> 00:15:46,350
I don't know either.
I just go back and forth.

273
00:15:47,450 --> 00:15:50,020
For crying out loud...

274
00:15:52,790 --> 00:15:55,830
Chairman Gong,
is there anything you can't do?

275
00:15:55,890 --> 00:15:58,900
I may not do it often,
but when I put my mind to something,

276
00:15:58,900 --> 00:16:00,860
I'm amazing at it. It's good, right?

277
00:16:02,300 --> 00:16:06,400
Cooking's about putting heart in.
Stop spitting.

278
00:16:06,470 --> 00:16:07,740
Close your mouth and concentrate.

279
00:16:08,740 --> 00:16:11,740
No one's fooled by your grandma act,
Chef Hong.

280
00:16:11,940 --> 00:16:15,780
But I'm in a great mood today,
so I'll let it slide just this once.

281
00:16:15,980 --> 00:16:18,250
- Yeong Soo! Cue the music.
- What?

282
00:16:18,250 --> 00:16:19,280
Oh, right. Okay.

283
00:16:23,390 --> 00:16:27,320
I'm so happy I could burst.
I mean, no matter what I do today,

284
00:16:27,320 --> 00:16:30,760
I'm in such a good mood. I love it.

285
00:16:30,830 --> 00:16:34,030
Are you happy your son is chairman,
my baby?

286
00:16:34,230 --> 00:16:38,340
Yes, I'm thrilled.
I'm just over the moon.

287
00:16:39,140 --> 00:16:41,310
- Stir!
- Yes, ma'am.

288
00:16:41,370 --> 00:16:42,440
Don't...

289
00:16:43,140 --> 00:16:44,610
Hey, come on...

290
00:16:45,510 --> 00:16:48,180
I've stepped down as chairman,
and I'm a nobody now.

291
00:16:49,350 --> 00:16:50,550
Is it still okay for you to work
for me?

292
00:16:50,650 --> 00:16:52,580
You are the spiritual anchor
of the Kunhyang Group.

293
00:16:53,080 --> 00:16:54,080
Nothing has changed.

294
00:16:54,920 --> 00:16:57,050
It's an honor
to continue working for you.

295
00:16:58,360 --> 00:16:59,420
Thank you...

296
00:17:00,460 --> 00:17:02,560
for willingly standing by my side.

297
00:17:03,330 --> 00:17:06,330
No, I'm the one who's grateful
for choosing me...

298
00:17:08,130 --> 00:17:09,970
and for freeing me from taking
Jin Tae Seok's orders...

299
00:17:11,870 --> 00:17:13,240
ever again.

300
00:17:16,170 --> 00:17:18,280
How is Mi Hyang doing?

301
00:17:19,880 --> 00:17:22,410
She's a strong and capable woman.

302
00:17:23,850 --> 00:17:26,050
Manager Hwang,
perhaps in Ki Beom's place,

303
00:17:27,750 --> 00:17:30,320
- you could be by Mi Hyang's side.
- I don't deserve that.

304
00:17:30,490 --> 00:17:31,820
I'm just...

305
00:17:34,930 --> 00:17:37,560
watching over her from a distance,
as a way of atoning.

306
00:17:45,640 --> 00:17:49,140
(Damga Charcoal Grill)

307
00:17:49,810 --> 00:17:52,010
What business do you have
in a shabby place like this?

308
00:18:04,020 --> 00:18:05,490
The meat has a nice, deep flavor.

309
00:18:05,620 --> 00:18:08,290
If you're done eating,
just get to the point.

310
00:18:11,130 --> 00:18:12,230
Our Jung Won...

311
00:18:13,360 --> 00:18:15,870
is still your
and Ki Beom's daughter.

312
00:18:15,930 --> 00:18:18,200
Why state the obvious
like it's some big secret?

313
00:18:19,070 --> 00:18:20,070
Did she tell you?

314
00:18:22,470 --> 00:18:23,510
Did Jung Won tell you...

315
00:18:24,640 --> 00:18:27,340
that Jin Tae Seok
is her biological father...

316
00:18:27,410 --> 00:18:29,110
That's complete nonsense.
Don't even say it.

317
00:18:29,580 --> 00:18:30,850
So what if
he's her biological father?

318
00:18:31,220 --> 00:18:32,920
That was just fate.

319
00:18:34,150 --> 00:18:37,590
I wonder why fate would be so cruel.

320
00:18:37,650 --> 00:18:41,760
A real bond is forged by facing life
together here on Earth.

321
00:18:41,930 --> 00:18:44,930
For over 30 years, Jung Won...

322
00:18:45,230 --> 00:18:48,330
has been my Ki Beom's daughter,
and that's how it'll always be.

323
00:18:49,600 --> 00:18:50,930
How can I ever...

324
00:18:51,970 --> 00:18:53,840
atone for what I did to him?

325
00:18:55,340 --> 00:18:57,670
Do I even deserve to?

326
00:18:59,140 --> 00:19:00,280
That story about Young Sun...

327
00:19:01,210 --> 00:19:02,410
was true.

328
00:19:03,680 --> 00:19:06,720
I heard you took the poison
meant for Jung Won,

329
00:19:07,320 --> 00:19:08,590
and it wasn't just an act.

330
00:19:11,560 --> 00:19:13,220
I want to be reborn.

331
00:19:15,260 --> 00:19:16,760
I'll make...

332
00:19:17,830 --> 00:19:19,500
Jin Tae Seok pay with my own hands.

333
00:19:22,130 --> 00:19:24,540
Then I'll help you.

334
00:19:25,140 --> 00:19:28,840
If it's to take down Jin Tae Seok,
I'd risk my own life.

335
00:19:30,840 --> 00:19:34,780
It's up to us mothers
to protect our kids.

336
00:19:35,810 --> 00:19:38,350
Mi Hyang. Please, help me.

337
00:19:40,720 --> 00:19:43,620
What do you need me to do?

338
00:19:50,760 --> 00:19:53,260
(Joo Ha Neul)

339
00:19:56,230 --> 00:19:58,200
So you'd even take out Joo Ha Neul?

340
00:20:01,870 --> 00:20:04,810
(Joo Ha Neul)

341
00:20:10,350 --> 00:20:11,450
Come on in.

342
00:20:18,460 --> 00:20:21,290
You invited me,
so I couldn't come empty-handed.

343
00:20:21,730 --> 00:20:25,000
Oh my, how did you know
I love flowers?

344
00:20:25,730 --> 00:20:27,230
You like flowers?

345
00:20:27,660 --> 00:20:30,130
When I got you flowers
on Parents' Day,

346
00:20:30,130 --> 00:20:32,140
you asked why
I was wasting my money.

347
00:20:32,200 --> 00:20:34,770
You always said you'd rather have
a steamed bun instead.

348
00:20:34,840 --> 00:20:38,740
When did I say that?
He remembers the most useless stuff.

349
00:20:38,940 --> 00:20:43,750
I don't know why flowers make me
so emotional these days.

350
00:20:44,110 --> 00:20:46,280
- Right?
- It's a sign you're getting older.

351
00:20:46,280 --> 00:20:50,020
I looked it up,
and photos of flowers...

352
00:20:50,020 --> 00:20:51,520
are the most common thing
in middle-aged women's profiles.

353
00:20:51,590 --> 00:20:55,460
Yeong Soo, what good is being smart
if you have no tact?

354
00:20:55,790 --> 00:20:58,760
- Do you want a beating with these?
- Stop...

355
00:20:59,060 --> 00:21:00,130
Calm down.

356
00:21:03,270 --> 00:21:08,210
This is a French short rib stew.
The wine aroma is incredible, right?

357
00:21:09,310 --> 00:21:12,340
Let's all have some mulled wine.

358
00:21:12,340 --> 00:21:13,480
You too, Ha Neul.

359
00:21:14,040 --> 00:21:15,080
And for you...

360
00:21:23,650 --> 00:21:25,390
It's warming me right up.

361
00:21:27,890 --> 00:21:30,060
The beef bourguignon is fantastic,
Chef Hong.

362
00:21:30,130 --> 00:21:33,830
I made this all myself.
Chef Hong just supervised.

363
00:21:33,960 --> 00:21:36,630
- Isn't that right, Chef Hong?
- That's right, Chairman Gong.

364
00:21:37,200 --> 00:21:40,400
She was so thrilled
that you became the chairman.

365
00:21:40,600 --> 00:21:42,910
I was afraid
she would take my job as chef.

366
00:21:44,010 --> 00:21:45,010
Goodness.

367
00:21:45,910 --> 00:21:47,310
Have some soup, too.

368
00:22:09,270 --> 00:22:10,270
Here.

369
00:22:12,400 --> 00:22:14,070
What made you want to come outside
all of a sudden?

370
00:22:20,780 --> 00:22:22,710
You're a truly good person.

371
00:22:24,450 --> 00:22:26,520
Not as good as you.

372
00:22:36,830 --> 00:22:37,930
I'm ready.

373
00:22:39,660 --> 00:22:41,770
I'll agree to anything
unless you say we should break up...

374
00:22:42,500 --> 00:22:45,840
because we're the children
of feuding families.

375
00:22:51,310 --> 00:22:52,340
I might...

376
00:22:53,980 --> 00:22:56,250
have to stab you in the back.

377
00:22:59,020 --> 00:23:01,350
I'll probably have to take you down.

378
00:23:02,650 --> 00:23:05,160
I'll have to drag you
from the chairman's seat...

379
00:23:06,390 --> 00:23:08,730
so that Jin Tae Seok
can make his comeback.

380
00:23:08,790 --> 00:23:10,360
Then do it, Jung Won.

381
00:23:13,900 --> 00:23:14,970
Ha Neul.

382
00:23:15,030 --> 00:23:18,030
The reason I was so determined to be
the chairman of Kunhyang Group...

383
00:23:18,170 --> 00:23:19,740
was to gain power.

384
00:23:22,240 --> 00:23:25,980
Power to destroy Jin Tae Seok,
the man who killed my father.

385
00:23:27,940 --> 00:23:29,650
And to protect you, Jung Won.

386
00:23:34,650 --> 00:23:35,990
I'm so sorry, Ha Neul.

387
00:23:50,400 --> 00:23:53,400
When will I be able to make sure
you never have to cry again?

388
00:23:55,270 --> 00:23:57,410
I want to get my revenge
on Jin Tae Seok soon...

389
00:23:57,970 --> 00:24:00,710
so the two of us can run away
somewhere far from here.

390
00:24:02,180 --> 00:24:03,710
That sounds wonderful.

391
00:24:22,570 --> 00:24:24,430
Hey, take it easy. Don't eat it all.

392
00:24:25,670 --> 00:24:27,440
Chef Hong, you have some too.

393
00:24:27,870 --> 00:24:28,870
I'm fine, thank you.

394
00:24:31,940 --> 00:24:35,250
This mulled wine is so good.
I'd love to learn how to make it.

395
00:24:35,550 --> 00:24:37,650
Chef Hong, could you write down
the recipe for me?

396
00:24:37,750 --> 00:24:39,820
Just give me a call
whenever you're craving it.

397
00:24:40,520 --> 00:24:42,990
A chef's recipe is a state secret.

398
00:24:44,190 --> 00:24:47,060
Then should I give you the recipe
I secretly jotted down earlier?

399
00:24:47,060 --> 00:24:48,090
Hey!

400
00:24:49,060 --> 00:24:50,830
You scared me.
Now you're Grandma again?

401
00:24:52,930 --> 00:24:54,000
What a joke.

402
00:24:55,430 --> 00:24:58,500
Young Chae, what is this getup?

403
00:24:58,870 --> 00:24:59,870
Pretty, isn't it?

404
00:25:02,740 --> 00:25:04,240
I didn't copy Jung Won's design.

405
00:25:05,010 --> 00:25:06,210
It's an original
Joo Young Chae design.

406
00:25:06,810 --> 00:25:07,810
It's great, isn't it?

407
00:25:13,480 --> 00:25:15,190
Young Chae, are you okay?

408
00:25:15,490 --> 00:25:18,120
Get off me.
Even a dog gets to eat in peace.

409
00:25:32,340 --> 00:25:35,310
It's mulled wine.
This might help you feel better.

410
00:25:35,570 --> 00:25:37,870
No, I can't. That's alcohol.
It has wine in it.

411
00:25:41,650 --> 00:25:43,980
Hey, Grandma, what's her deal?

412
00:25:43,980 --> 00:25:46,180
Young Chae, are you okay?

413
00:25:47,820 --> 00:25:49,090
Quit telling me off!

414
00:25:49,920 --> 00:25:52,160
What did I do that was so wrong?
Why are you always on my case?

415
00:25:54,090 --> 00:25:55,930
Are you that happy
that Ha Neul is the chairman now?

416
00:25:57,830 --> 00:25:58,860
I'm your biological daughter,

417
00:25:59,700 --> 00:26:01,970
but I'm a complete
and total mess now.

418
00:26:02,830 --> 00:26:04,600
You're the worst one of all.

419
00:26:04,900 --> 00:26:06,170
- Hey!
- Young Chae.

420
00:26:06,170 --> 00:26:07,600
- Let me go!
- Come on out.

421
00:26:07,600 --> 00:26:10,670
I said to leave me alone!

422
00:26:22,890 --> 00:26:23,890
What's wrong with Young Chae?

423
00:26:25,090 --> 00:26:26,160
She's been acting
a little strange lately.

424
00:26:26,890 --> 00:26:29,930
She's been dressing weird
and didn't even recognize me.

425
00:26:31,290 --> 00:26:33,230
She took it hard
when I didn't become the chairman.

426
00:26:34,000 --> 00:26:35,530
And she got fired
from the Design Team.

427
00:26:38,340 --> 00:26:41,070
You must be happy that
Joo Ha Neul...

428
00:26:41,570 --> 00:26:42,570
is the new chairman.

429
00:26:44,110 --> 00:26:47,140
I still have feelings for Ha Neul,
but it’s not the same as before.

430
00:26:47,610 --> 00:26:50,550
It's more like, "He was capable,
so he got the position." That's all.

431
00:26:51,250 --> 00:26:54,450
I don't think
we can just let this go.

432
00:26:55,190 --> 00:26:56,290
Not if we care about Kunhyang.

433
00:26:57,520 --> 00:26:58,620
Did something happen?

434
00:26:58,620 --> 00:27:01,860
Dad planned to make me
the new chairman.

435
00:27:02,330 --> 00:27:03,930
Those who are
on his side and mine...

436
00:27:04,530 --> 00:27:05,860
provided solid support.

437
00:27:08,400 --> 00:27:11,270
But Joo Ha Neul bribed
the board members...

438
00:27:11,840 --> 00:27:12,940
and turned the tables.

439
00:27:13,540 --> 00:27:16,070
No way.
Ha Neul's not that kind of person.

440
00:27:16,210 --> 00:27:17,610
You can't just believe what you see
on the surface.

441
00:27:18,310 --> 00:27:21,110
Joo Ha Neul colluded
with foreign investors...

442
00:27:22,180 --> 00:27:24,250
and secured another ten percent
of Kunhyang's stock.

443
00:27:24,810 --> 00:27:26,850
- And I have proof.
- Ten percent?

444
00:27:27,920 --> 00:27:29,650
Then isn't his stake
similar to yours?

445
00:27:29,920 --> 00:27:32,320
With Chairman Gong's shares,
that's 17 percent.

446
00:27:33,360 --> 00:27:34,620
The two of them
planned this together.

447
00:27:36,030 --> 00:27:39,160
They're stealing the company
our family fought hard to protect.

448
00:27:42,630 --> 00:27:43,700
This is a full-blown crisis.

449
00:27:47,400 --> 00:27:48,810
By any chance,

450
00:27:49,710 --> 00:27:51,340
has Dad ever mentioned
a Swiss account to you?

451
00:27:52,280 --> 00:27:53,810
What's that?

452
00:27:55,380 --> 00:27:56,510
Since you're his favorite,

453
00:27:57,280 --> 00:27:58,850
I assumed he would've told you.

454
00:28:02,390 --> 00:28:04,190
It's a fund that Father
has been managing on the side,

455
00:28:05,520 --> 00:28:07,860
but it's completely firewalled
from any outside access.

456
00:28:08,220 --> 00:28:09,230
He had something like that?

457
00:28:09,630 --> 00:28:12,700
We have to use that money
to acquire more Kunhyang stock.

458
00:28:13,530 --> 00:28:14,760
Then why don't you just tell Dad?

459
00:28:15,270 --> 00:28:16,800
I don't know if he fell
for Chairman Gong's ploy or what,

460
00:28:17,070 --> 00:28:18,500
but all he says is that
it's not the right time.

461
00:28:19,300 --> 00:28:20,300
It's driving me crazy.

462
00:28:23,270 --> 00:28:24,910
All I need is the password.

463
00:28:26,340 --> 00:28:27,880
He must have written
it down somewhere.

464
00:28:32,520 --> 00:28:34,150
If we're going to get Dad back
on his feet,

465
00:28:35,020 --> 00:28:36,720
you and I need to work together.

466
00:29:10,120 --> 00:29:11,120
(Enter your PIN)

467
00:29:12,060 --> 00:29:13,060
(Incorrect PIN)

468
00:29:14,020 --> 00:29:15,230
It's not Dad's birthday.

469
00:29:16,860 --> 00:29:17,930
Mom's birthday?

470
00:29:19,560 --> 00:29:20,560
(Incorrect PIN)

471
00:29:22,870 --> 00:29:23,900
Or maybe my birthday?

472
00:29:25,440 --> 00:29:26,440
(Incorrect PIN)

473
00:29:27,570 --> 00:29:28,770
As if.

474
00:29:30,110 --> 00:29:31,670
Maybe it's not four digits?

475
00:29:33,540 --> 00:29:34,540
Don't tell me...

476
00:29:48,760 --> 00:29:50,830
(Mr. Kim, Switzerland)

477
00:30:01,800 --> 00:30:03,140
Se Mi, what's wrong?

478
00:30:03,610 --> 00:30:05,380
I don't know what to do.

479
00:30:05,610 --> 00:30:06,910
Tell me. Take your time.

480
00:30:08,110 --> 00:30:10,610
Se Hoon told me
Dad has a Swiss account,

481
00:30:10,680 --> 00:30:12,680
and he wanted me
to find out the password.

482
00:30:22,090 --> 00:30:23,290
It's 2.3 billion dollars.

483
00:30:24,690 --> 00:30:25,700
It's 2.3 billion dollars.

484
00:30:28,300 --> 00:30:30,470
I have the password
to Dad's Swiss account.

485
00:30:32,940 --> 00:30:34,440
Now, Kunhyang is mine.

486
00:30:36,470 --> 00:30:38,610
The password to the Swiss account?

487
00:30:38,840 --> 00:30:40,710
If we know it,

488
00:30:41,610 --> 00:30:43,150
we could take Jin Tae Seok down
in one fell swoop.

489
00:30:44,280 --> 00:30:45,580
Tell me something I don't know.

490
00:30:45,880 --> 00:30:47,920
But how on earth are you going
to find it out?

491
00:30:48,120 --> 00:30:49,420
I've failed once before.

492
00:30:50,950 --> 00:30:51,960
But this time...

493
00:30:53,490 --> 00:30:54,790
I think I've succeeded.

494
00:30:56,990 --> 00:30:58,700
You're saying
we have it in our hands?

495
00:31:16,780 --> 00:31:19,750
(A Graceful Liar)

496
00:31:41,900 --> 00:31:43,440
Did you already stash it somewhere?

497
00:31:43,440 --> 00:31:44,670
I'm the one managing it.

498
00:31:44,770 --> 00:31:46,180
What are you all scheming?

499
00:31:46,180 --> 00:31:48,280
We have to take down
Honorary Chairman Jin Tae Seok.

500
00:31:48,380 --> 00:31:50,510
Chairman Joo Ha Neul's reign
won't last long.

501
00:31:50,580 --> 00:31:52,480
We don't have enough justification
to turn the tables.

502
00:31:52,550 --> 00:31:55,150
Se Hoon will oust Ha Neul
and become the chairman soon.

503
00:31:55,220 --> 00:31:57,120
Because he now has
the world's most powerful weapon.

504
00:31:57,190 --> 00:32:00,390
Jin Tae Seok isn't the type
to give up his power that easily.

505
00:32:00,590 --> 00:32:03,290
Hye Ra is definitely plotting something
behind my back.

506
00:32:06,530 --> 00:32:08,560
(Subtitles are provided by KOCOWA.)
